---
title: North Indian Turkey Curry with lentils and wilted spinach
description: This dish's nutritious turkey mince and simmered lentils are seasoned with a brilliant blend of spices typically found in North Indian cuisine. Fenugreek, turmeric and ground coriander all make an appearance!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W10_IE_IEXCQLT18826-2_Main__6high-10f337b8.jpg
